# 🛡️ Yume no Katsubō - Backend API

This is the backend API for the **Yume no Katsubō** puzzle game — built with **Node.js + Express**, connected to **MongoDB**, and hosted on **Render**.

---

## 🌐 Live API Endpoint

👉 [https://yume-backend-rabiya.onrender.com/api/characters](https://yume-backend-rabiya.onrender.com/api/characters)

Returns:
```json
[
  {
    "name": "Yash",
    "role": "Strategic puzzle master"
  },
  {
    "name": "Shiro",
    "role": "Wise and logical companion"
  },
  {
    "name": "Rebz",
    "role": "Glowing heroine (unlocked)",
    "unlockable": true
  }
]

⚙️ Tech Stack
Node.js

Express.js

MongoDB Atlas

Render (Hosting)

dotenv for secure env vars

yume-backend/
├── server.js
├── models/
│   └── character.js
├── routes/
│   └── characters.js
└── .env
